00:01:21.254 --> 00:01:26.093 position:7% line:89% align:start
♪ But with spring in my heart

00:01:26.127 --> 00:01:28.230 position:19% line:89% align:start
♪ When seasons change

00:01:28.263 --> 00:01:29.831 position:16% line:89% align:start
♪ I'll change with them

